seo: SpringCloudConfig,目录遍历漏洞,CVE-2019-3799,检测,漏洞扫描
summary: 该插件用于检测SpringCloudConfig服务器是否存在CVE-2019-3799目录遍历漏洞，通过发送特定payload验证漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the SpringCloudConfig server has the CVE-2019-3799 directory traversal vulnerability by sending specific payloads to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
